description:
Wes is from Portland and he was very excited to visit San Diego.
"It's cloudy all the time and it rains a lot," he said, referring to his home town. "I love all this sunshine."
Wes has a sexy muscular body with some interesting tattoos. He has a wing on each forearm.
"Why did you decide to get those?" I asked him.
"No reason," he said. "I just thought they'd look cool."
I really liked his legs — they're really hairy!
I get the feeling that he might be gay or bi, but I'm not certain.
title: Wes
